      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1777383063606,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "text": "LitePack leads on KSR at every budget level (90.3%→90.8%→93.4% as budget relaxes) and scores highest overall (90.8% vs 90.3–90.5%).\nKSR measures how completely query keywords are covered by the packed context — LitePack's γ×keyword_coverage factor directly optimizes this,\nwhile Similarity and MMR have no explicit keyword alignment term.",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "LitePack leads on KSR at every budget level (90.3%→90.8%→93.4% as budget relaxes) and scores highest overall (90.8% vs 90.3–90.5%).\nKSR measures how completely query keywords are covered by the packed context — LitePack's γ×keyword_coverage factor directly optimizes this,\nwhile Similarity and MMR have no explicit keyword alignment term.",
      "lineHeight": 1.35,
      "version": 2,
